ExBingo
=======

ExBingo is a NeoForge port and derivative version of Yet Another Bingo.

Upstream project:
- Name: Yet Another Bingo
- Modrinth: https://modrinth.com/mod/yet-another-minecraft-bingo
- Source: https://gitlab.com/horrificdev/bingo
- License: GNU Lesser General Public License v3.0 only (LGPL-3.0-only)

This project keeps portions of the upstream code, resources, data files, translations,
and package structure while adapting the mod for NeoForge under the `exbingo` public
mod id and resource namespace.

Credits:
- Yet Another Bingo by horrificdev and contributors.
- Bingo Card HUD and "Bingo!" button textures by marceles.
- Portions of the original project were inspired by Extremelyd1/minecraft-bingo.
- Translations were contributed through the upstream CrowdIn project and its community.

